      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 32
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_6",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "Hey there! Honestly, you won't believe how gorgeous this car is. I\u2019ve babied it since day one, and it still looks and smells like it just rolled off the showroom floor! Not a single scratch or dent anywhere\u2014it's absolutely pristine. I\u2019m sad to see it go, but I know the next owner is going to have a blast with it. Come take a look, you're going to love it!",
      "price": 44500.0,
