    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_11_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_11",
      "description": "Offered is an exceptional 2004 BMW M3 (E46) featuring the legendary S54 3.2L inline-six engine and a crisp ZF 6-speed manual transmission. This collector-grade specimen is mechanically sorted, boasting a comprehensive VANOS overhaul and a reinforced rear subframe utilizing Turner Motorsport plates to ensure long-term structural rigidity. The high-revving power plant utilizes individual throttle bodies for surgical response, while the chassis remains perfectly poised on Bilstein B16 adjustable dampers and a factory M-Variable limited-slip differential. The exterior retains its deep, original luster with zero oxidation, complemented by an interior with supple Nappa leather and perfect tactile switchgear. This is a turn-key example with zero deferred maintenance and no structural compromises.",
